<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.216.91032.figure23>
    dc:description "Figure 23. Microlicia laniflora A habit B leaf abaxial surface C bracteole abaxial surface D flower in lateral view E flowering hypanthium F petal adaxial surface G detail of indumentum on the apex of the petal H antepetalous (behind) and antesepalous (in front) stamens I gynoecium J ovary in cross-section K capsule enveloped by the hypanthium. Drawn from Almeda et al. 7726 (UEC) and Almeda et al. 9197 (UEC)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/784274" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

